      "bgName": "hoshimisyouzi"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ある日の残業時間",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh001.wav",
      "text": "（今日も残業か……\n出来れば仕事じゃなく、プライベートで\n莉央さんと二人きりの時間を過ごしたいよ）",
      "startTime": 2.1000000358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_companyoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimisyouzi"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-rio001.wav",
      "text": "こら、{user}君……\nサボってないで仕事しなさい……",
      "startTime": 10.1000000358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_companyoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimisyouzi"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh002.wav",
      "text": "は、はい！　すみません！\n……って、あれ？　莉央さん？",
      "startTime": 13.5666667025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_companyoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimisyouzi"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-rio002.wav",
      "text": "うーん……\nほら、ここ間違ってるわよ……\nすー、すー……",
      "startTime": 19.5666667025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh003.wav",
      "text": "椅子に座ったまま寝てる……？\n莉央さんでも仕事中に居眠りすることが\nあるんだな",
      "startTime": 30.1333333691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_companyoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimisyouzi"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh004.wav",
      "text": "と言うか、莉央さんは夢の中でも俺を\n叱ってるのか……\n莉央さん、起きて下さい！",
      "startTime": 37.3000000358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_companyoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimisyouzi"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-rio003.wav",
      "text": "うーん……\nもうちょっと寝かせて……あと五分……",
      "startTime": 46.4000000358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh005.wav",
      "text": "全然起きる気配がない……\n残業続きで疲れてるんだろうな\n莉央さんが寝れるなら俺は……",
      "startTime": 52.9333333691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop"
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "今ならサボってもバレないぞ",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh006.wav",
              "text": "莉央さんだって居眠りしてるんだから\n俺も少しくらいサボってもいいよな\nよし、ちょっと休憩するか……",
              "startTime": 62.2333333691,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-rio004.wav",
              "text": "ダメでしょ……\n起きなさい……\nほら、早く起きて……",
              "startTime": 72.5333328605,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-rio005.wav",
              "text": "いい加減にしなさい\nいつまで寝てるつもり？\nさっさと起きなさい！",
              "startTime": 81.7666692455,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 7166.666666699995
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh007.wav",
              "text": "はいぃぃぃっ！！\n……え？　あれ？\nもしかして俺……",
              "startTime": 88.9333359122,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-rio006.wav",
              "text": "随分と気持ち良さそうに寝てたわね\n私と二人きりの時間が\nそんなに退屈だったのかしら",
              "startTime": 94.8666692455,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh008.wav",
              "text": "す、すみません！　すぐに残業の続きを……\nあれ？　俺の分の仕事が全部終わってる\nもしかして寝ている間に莉央さんが……",
              "startTime": 103.6333359122,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-rio007.wav",
              "text": "ほら、もう遅いから、今日は帰るわよ\n貴方も早く帰って休みなさい",
              "startTime": 115.1333394726,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh009.wav",
              "text": "（もしかして、俺が疲れて寝ていると\n思った莉央さんは、気を遣って\n俺の分まで仕事を……）",
              "startTime": 122.4333394726,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh010.wav",
              "text": "（くそ、失敗した。俺が莉央さんに負担を\n掛けてどうするんだ。俺が頑張って\n莉央さんを助けなきゃいけないのに……）",
              "startTime": 129.066672806,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "今なら莉央さんに悪戯してもバレないかな？",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a"
            },
            {
              "type": "sfx",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
              "startTime": 142.166666158
            },
            {
              "type": "sfx",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
              "startTime": 143.8099994914
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh011.wav",
              "text": "今なら莉央さんに触れても怒られないよな？\nよし、そーっと近づいて……\n起こさないように優しく頭を撫でて……",
              "startTime": 137.166672806,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 8799.985865799983
                },
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 9466.660018799985
                },
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 17233.32668539999
                },
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 17900.00083839999
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh012.wav",
              "text": "莉央さんの髪、サラサラだな\n触り心地が良くて\nいつまででも撫でていられるよ",
              "startTime": 147.6000061393,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-rio008.wav",
              "text": "ふふ……{user}君……\nもっと、撫でて……",
              "startTime": 155.566672806,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh013.wav",
              "text": "え？　寝てる……よな？\nじゃあ、今のは寝言？\n夢の中で俺におねだりをしているのか？",
              "startTime": 161.0000061393,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-rio009.wav",
              "text": "{user}君の手\n大きくて、あったかい……\n私、この手……好きよ……",
              "startTime": 171.5000061393,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh014.wav",
              "text": "俺に髪を撫でられて、莉央さんが幸せそうに\n笑っている。普段の隙のない莉央さんとは\n全然違う、無防備で優しい微笑みだ",
              "startTime": 181.6666758578,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh015.wav",
              "text": "……莉央さん、お疲れ様\n俺はずっとそばにいますから、安心して\nゆっくり休んで下さい",
              "startTime": 192.0666758578,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-rio010.wav",
              "text": "うん……{user}君……\nありがとう……\nすー、すー……",
              "startTime": 200.3333425244,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh016.wav",
              "text": "さてと、莉央さんが寝ている間に\n莉央さんの分まで仕事を終わらせるか",
              "startTime": 208.6666758578,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh017.wav",
              "text": "恋って凄いな\n大好きな人のために頑張ろうって思うだけで\n元気が湧いてくる気がするよ",
              "startTime": 214.8333425244,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 223.266666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh018.wav",
      "text": "はぁ、今日は仕事に身が入らなかったな\nそれもこれも、莉央さんが大阪に出張に\n行っていて、一度も顔を見ていないせいだ",
      "startTime": 225.3333496452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/lovestoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_05_01-koh019.wav",
      "text": "莉央さん、今頃は大阪で残業中かな？\nせめて声を聞きたいけど\n今電話を掛けたら迷惑だろうか？",
      "startTime": 235.9000163119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "莉央に電話を掛ける",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_stm-01.m4a"
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": null,
              "speakerName": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": null,
